  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"https://ollama.com/assets/library/deepseek-v2/9422627b-6d24-401b-8d49-5d316df9956b\" width=\"320\"/></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Note: this model requires <a href=\"https://github.com/ollama/ollama/releases/tag/v0.1.40\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ollama 0.1.40</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>DeepSeek-V2 is a a strong Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) language model characterized by economical training and efficient inference.</p>\n\n<p>Note: this model is bilingual in English and Chinese.</p>\n\n<p>The model comes in two sizes:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>16B Lite: <code>ollama run deepseek-v2:16b</code></li>\n<li>236B: <code>ollama run deepseek-v2:236b</code></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2\" rel=\"nofollow\">GitHub</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
